                Your Go-To Guide For Creating An Employee Handbook
              </h2> <div class="w-full h-[24px]"></div> <div class="flex md:flex-row flex-col items-center"><div class="w-[48px] h-[48px] overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-lavender"><picture>  <source type="image/webp" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/60x60/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png, https://img2.storyblok.com/120x120/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png 2x"> <source srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/60x60/filters:format(png):quality(75)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png, https://img2.storyblok.com/120x120/filters:format(png):quality(75)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png 2x"> <img src="https://img2.storyblok.com/60x60/filters:format(png):quality(75)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></picture> <!----> <!----></div> <div class="h-[16px] w-full md:w-[24px] md:h-full"></div> <p class="text-[16px] text-light-gray leading-[24px] tracking-[0.15px] md:text-white">
