                CULTURE
              </p></div></div></div> <div class="h-[6px] md:h-[8px]"></div> <p class="text-[12px] text-light-gray leading-[20px] md:text-[14px] md:leading-[24px] tracking-[0.4px] md:tracking-[0.1px]">
          01 Jun 2021
        </p> <div class="h-[8px] md:h-[20px] lg:h-[24px]"></div> <h3 class="font-700 text-charcoal text-[16px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[24px] md:leading-[32px] tracking-[0.15px]">
          What Is The Cultural Web Model?
        </h3> <div class="h-[8px] md:h-[20px] lg:h-[24px]"></div> <p class="text-[13px] leading-[20px] text-light-gray md:text-[16px] md:leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">
          Organizational culture has a massive influence on an organization&#x2019;s performance. Even though, there are many organizations that may not manage or stimulate their own culture, a culture in any company can be extremely telling when it comes to looking at the future of the business.
